      • processEnv

        public void processEnv()
        This method is responsible for updating the current greenhouse environment after the effects of external effects intelligently. Each environment property of the greenhouse has a specified maximum and minimum threshold beyond which the external effects will have no effect. For example, the temperature cannot go below absolute zero and air cannot be saturated past 100% for humidity.
